column3: “Quite the trouvaille! The subtle onset of bliss skillfully weaved through my soul with each passing of time; metanoia. It is a serene strain, for when one is utiwaaien. This is the most orphic strain I have ever come across in all of my travels. It just gives off such a eleutheromania. Now that it is all gone, the vorfreude is nearly overwhelming.”

“Great smell & taste 
Very sweet aroma 
If you haven't tried, you're missing out”
“Got this as a ftp preroll, put me right to sleep at night and woke me right up the next day. Stayed productive while feeling great. Will return...”
